content:
You can now create and manage copy field enrichments for contacts, leads, accounts, and assets. Previously, you could only manage copy field enrichments for Contact and Lead objects in Object Manager. Calculated insight objects (CIO) must have a single, Individual ID as the dimension, but you canâ€™t use multidimensional objects.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This feature is available starting in August 2024.

How: From Setup, select Integrations, Enrichments, and then Copy Fields.
title: Use More Objects for Copy Field Enrichments
